unacloud.share.enums

  • Packages that use unacloud.share.enums 
    Package Description
    unacloud.share.db
    In this package are located all classes to connect and execute SQL commands in database.
    unacloud.share.entities
    In this package are located all entities required to process transactions in database.
    unacloud.share.enums
    In this package are located all enums shared by server projects.
    unacloud.share.queue
    In this package are located all classes to manage communication among projects using queues.
